HEADWORD: Sweetness
<hw>Sweet"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>sw⟦emac⟧tness</ets>.]</ety> <def>The quality or state of being
sweet (in any sense of the adjective); gratefulness to the taste or to
the smell; agreeableness.</def>⟦br⟧
